Emma Tate (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emma_Tate_(actress) 0 Emma Tate is a British voice actress known for many roles, including being the voice of Perfect Peter in Horrid Henry, the title character Harry in Harry and His Bucket Full of Dinosaurs, Raggles and Bluebird in Everything's Rosie, and Mowgli in The Jungle Book. She's also been the voices of Katsuma, Luvli in Moshi Monsters: The Movie and Kipper in The Magic Key.
